{"tid":1958840,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得撈麵來講，台灣曾拌麵屌打哂所有香港印尼日本韓國的撈面？","createTime":"2020-04-05T03:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T15:31:20.000Z","uid":118346,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f8e7a7e0f6c505bf4bb3136c287d5744060097","tid":1958840,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/214008_bf777d3ad9cdb542166ad6ae271c579e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F214008_bf777d3ad9cdb542166ad6ae271c579e.jpg&h=04c42e7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n麵質出色，花椒味又香，加多隻水煮蛋&amp;生菜絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不服來辯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ccbdd40d968e91b5ece65ee5067fd7184de6649","tid":1958840,"uid":321977,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"印尼撈麵無撚敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e530187413b7cb8c7e1ea65214c6ce3d4d87a7","tid":1958840,"uid":125168,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:43:33.000Z","msg":"冇，印尼贏曬"},{"pid":"d99c8509013ec413bfc4978ac040566e24b27e42","tid":1958840,"uid":112241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:45:37.000Z","msg":"食個兩包配料姐，唔駛吹咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n面質黎講，大靚平價面屌打佢，醬料自己溝好食過佢好多<br />\n性價比極低。"},{"pid":"99da5d5e020f3c38e4fc178dc6e9f1ac55770bde","tid":1958840,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"印尼食到厭<img src=\"/assets/faces